overview: BFF's, Kenzie (Kenzie Reeves) and Haley (Haley Reed) hatch a plan to test the fidelity of their boyfriends (Donnie Rock), (Codey Steele). The girls decide that each would try to seduce the other's boyfriend to see if they would remain faithful. They soon discover that their boyfriends aren't quite as loyal as they had thought!
title: Game of Seduction
